Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同盟軍的艦隊\N馬上就要進入交戰空域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.41,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}棄子\NResign
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方射程極限12哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降速度過快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.20,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就保持這個下降速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.37,0:01:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下降到可以用目測進行交戰的\N可能距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE表面發生變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是觸手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前發生大量爆炸閃光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於視線不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用目測判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.95,0:01:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE的觸手正不分敵我的\N在攻擊附近船艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左翼戴汀號，莊嚴號遭擊沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.73,0:01:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在兩分鐘裡我方的戰艦\N就被擊沈了四分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會變成消耗戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.80,0:01:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭就是消耗戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使流再多的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要趁現在讓世界\N從基爾特的統治下獲得解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把艾兒薇絲‧漢彌爾敦\N和第四個關鍵謎詩到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.41,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能把EXILE的系統\N自戴芬妮的控制下切離出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此，即使會失去所有戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也必須打倒戴芬妮總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方戰艦維持原速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入戰鬥行列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，又擊沈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇隊出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了，在這種視線下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩開觸手殺出一條血路來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夥拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反應挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，不可以理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，要輸掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點鐘方向有雨候鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到終點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨候鳥曉得路在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，要輸掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要順著風走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們贏過英麥曼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為我叫你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為我叫你下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界也走到了盡頭是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖中那扇巨大的門打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE加快了下降速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方旗艦還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲毫不見損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有時間猶豫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破戰線，直搗戴芬妮總帥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會保護您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變艦隊陣形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有戰艦都已並排在本艦兩舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著烏爾班號，第三航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，戴芬妮總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.71,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是迪奧也在的話\N一定會更有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我們的皇帝來開路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體戰艦，開始砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE放出的觸手的聲音\N太多了數不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有砲門準備發射\N定時信管魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備魚雷，定時信管12秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5秒就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撞到烏爾班號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開一至三號主砲塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，我方戰艦烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船員退到船艦前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.94,0:07:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向仰角20度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力全開，最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，打倒總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，這樣才漂亮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們被觸手包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體砲門發射噴射破甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算用拖的也要前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不清楚方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時\N她看著正步向死亡的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉絲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漸減口徑式重高角砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從戴芬妮的船上\N聽到了艦長的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛向天空...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，兩點鐘方向有一道光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用加速裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.37,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能在這時候發生紅視現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大風暴區...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我們越過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是度西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...是度西斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，妳害怕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮艦的殘骸要撞到地面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員準備下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位的戰鬥配置可以解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶我到EXILE那裡去，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長，請下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葳娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長...他說了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喊了蘇菲亞...\N副艦長您的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，葳娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是克勞士機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於越過了大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天空的彼方存在的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.82,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指引迷路的孩子\N回到母親手中的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫育生命萬物之氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麥之大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使降落的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是巨大的風之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在記憶的彼方存在的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切回歸的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人還真是不輕言放棄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.18,0:17:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後我永遠還是你的副官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖的畫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，葛溫他都哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒哭，這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你這大叔沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是大叔來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲，請帶我一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他們倆大概是覺得寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們誰不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔又哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這滴滴落的玩意是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頂級水啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.03,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在EXILE內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了爸爸他們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸他們的委託筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們倆獨處一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們努力到了最後一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間已沒有\N安那托勒和度西斯之分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不分基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們出發那天所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒有紛爭的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後要靠我們大家一起來打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是要抓對時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來了，瞌睡蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，吃午飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃午飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要飛囉，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該吃午飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流動的白雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拂過臉頰的一陣涼風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.78,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這片藍天裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論多高，無論多遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可以自由飛翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.07,0:22:25.50,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無際天空的彼方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}果てない空の彼方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.57,0:22:31.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切將連向何方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}すべては何処へ続くだろう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.51,0:22:37.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,追尋一處平靜的地方\N{\c&HFFBF00&}求める安らぎの場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.38,0:22:43.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,天使降落的路\N{\c&HFFBF00&}天使が降りる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.22,0:22:52.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信就連在我的手上\N{\c&HFFBF00&}腕へ　きっと続くよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.13,0:22:57.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:03.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
